{"tid":2345828,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"強烈寒潮正式襲港 除夕元旦北區恐4°C 下周再凍過 氣溫如坐過山車","createTime":"2020-12-30T00:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:48:41.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56846457542204a9580608100d5ec06f6aa410c4","tid":2345828,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:06:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/DGUN5XRWDJCBTFHHF6S4DHJQS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FDGUN5XRWDJCBTFHHF6S4DHJQS4%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGXdC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=9e182cf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FDGUN5XRWDJCBTFHHF6S4DHJQS4%2F&h=d2767dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/DGUN5XRWDJCBTFHHF6S4DHJQS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>強烈寒潮正式襲港 除夕元旦北區恐4&deg;C 下周再凍過 氣溫如坐過山車</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n強烈寒潮開始襲港，天文台預計市區氣溫會由12月30日凌晨最高約22&deg;C，急跌至早上約12&deg;C，日間雖回升至約16&deg;C，但晚上再回落至約10&deg;C的寒冷水平；31日除夕早上更降至約7&deg;C的嚴寒水平，新界再低兩三度。除夕日間持續寒冷，市區氣溫僅回升至約12&deg;C；1月1日元旦早上再跌至約8&deg;C，相當寒冷，電腦預報指北區連日僅4&deg;C。雖然元旦隨後幾日氣溫回升，但另一股冬季季候風下周中抵港，再度轉冷，市區連日跌至約12&deg;C。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Dgf9lXEd1TcfNw5BaLmzfgmT5ko=/802x649/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MQ6IRLHOHJAMNLM7UWTSRUYGJE.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDgf9lXEd1TcfNw5BaLmzfgmT5ko%3D%2F802x649%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMQ6IRLHOHJAMNLM7UWTSRUYGJE.png%3F&h=8be09708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>天文台預計市區氣溫在除夕早上降至約7&deg;C的嚴寒水平，新界再低兩三度。除夕日間持續寒冷，市區氣溫僅回升至約12&deg;C；1月1日元旦早上再跌至約8&deg;C。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Gpg4qnmBk7097hLxdTYO23tDnpI=/802x926/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NYKUZZCK75DXHAKOCMKOMHOIXI.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGpg4qnmBk7097hLxdTYO23tDnpI%3D%2F802x926%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNYKUZZCK75DXHAKOCMKOMHOIXI.png%3F&h=974beec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>天文台電腦預報指，新界部份地區在除夕和元旦僅4&deg;C。</em><br />\n<br />\n天文台在12月29日下午4時許提早發出寒冷天氣警告。雖然當時市區氣溫仍逾23&deg;C，尚算溫暖，但強烈寒潮穩定向廣東沿岸步步進逼。而其「先頭部隊」、冷鋒29日在華中形成，30日凌晨2時橫過廣東沿岸；本港風勢顯著增強，天文台亦發出強烈季候風信號。雖然香港市區在30日凌晨近1時仍高達22&deg;C，但廣州已跌至12&deg;C的寒冷水平，韶關更跌至6&deg;C的嚴寒水平，反映冷空氣已集結在廣州一帶，相當接近香港，隨時南壓過境。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qWzObO-UbzPWhdofwSHMhdkh6DA=/802x492/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/73TKRJTOIZGYHKII6EFJU7SW2Y.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqWzObO-UbzPWhdofwSHMhdkh6DA%3D%2F802x492%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F73TKRJTOIZGYHKII6EFJU7SW2Y.png%3F&h=3d82beca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>雖然香港市區在30日凌晨近1時仍高達22&deg;C，但廣州已跌至12&deg;C的寒冷水平，韶關更跌至6&deg;C的嚴寒水平，反映冷空氣已集結在廣州一帶，相當接近香港，隨時南壓過境。</em><br />\n<br />\n今次強烈寒潮除要抵禦嚴寒，亦要做好擋風和保濕，防止體溫流失和皮膚爆拆。天文台預計，12月30日普遍地區吹清勁至強風程度北風，離岸海域及高地吹烈風；31日除夕的風勢雖稍為緩和，但普遍地區仍吹清勁程度北風，離岸海域及高地初時吹強風，風勢有時頗大。至於12月31日除夕和1月1日元旦的相對濕度，則會跌至30-35%，非常乾燥。<br />\n<br />\n記者 李鈺廷"},{"pid":"39c84484866166d43fc3e8790827c215beaddb10","tid":2345828,"uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:07:46.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀:<strong><ins>天文台以最壞情況推算 2020年香港無冬天</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2345769\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2345769</a>"},{"pid":"d35ec2ba592c169773c0c030766120c98eb6c824","tid":2345828,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39c84484866166d43fc3e8790827c215beaddb10","tid":2345828,"uid":75050,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"reply